<div class="fixed top-25 right-0 p-4 bg-light-azure-200 rounded shadow-md border border-purple-600 z-index-50 mb-4 w-1/3">

    <h1 class="font-bold text-2xl">⚡🌩️⚡ <%= Article.emoji %>Last 10 cached Articles</h1>

    <ul>
    <% @last_ten_articles.each do |article| %>
        <li>
            ⌛️  <b><%= link_to article.hhmm, article %></b> <%= link_to article.title, article %>
                <% article.categories.each do |c| %>
                <%=    render_fancy_category(c) %>
                <% end %>
                <i>(<%= time_ago_in_words(article.published_date) rescue '🤷🏼‍♀️' %> ago )</i>
        </li>
    <% end %>
    </ul>

    <p></p>
    <p>⌚ Soon no caching, but in real-time updates via ActionCable! I just need to study ActionCable give me a break!</p>

</div>
